{"tid":1089706,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"美國司法部警告奧斯卡 杯葛Netflix或涉壟斷","createTime":"2019-04-03T03:32:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-03T04:01:02.000Z","uid":41343,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6d29d0d851a9cc50202dc6906349581c2b637db1","tid":1089706,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T03:32:48.000Z","msg":"奧斯卡頒獎機構據報正計劃加設障礙, 阻止串流媒體Netflix的作品再次角逐金像獎, 被美國司法部反壟斷部門提出警告.<br />\n<br />\n美國電影藝術與科學學院理事會, 將於23日召開年度頒獎規則會議. 消息指, 司法部去信學院, 指出透過更改頒獎規則, 來排除新興競爭對手的做法, 可能會引發反壟斷憂慮.<br />\n<br />\n學院發言人證實收到司法部的信, 並會作出相應回應. 但有理事會成員, 對於司法部介入奧斯卡頒獎禮表示驚訝, 質疑為何學院不能自行制定規則.<br />\n<br />\n在上屆頒獎禮中, Netflix的電影《羅馬》, 奪得最佳導演和最佳外語片等大獎. 但被部分學院成員質疑, 無電影票房的影片, 是否符合電影資格.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/default.aspx?NewsId=20190403072653\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Fdefault.aspx%3FNewsId%3D20190403072653&d=hsG%2BTWPyVhMSOc%2FhwZgu%2Bkv%2FgUeHX8FRhdV3zHjzpFI%3D&h=1d7af58b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/default.aspx?NewsId=20190403072653</a>"},{"pid":"bce71e0d9a9925994e3c81a22282b1ecc33bebbd","tid":1089706,"uid":31525,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T03:43:24.000Z","msg":"票房又唔係得獎準則<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解唔算電影"},{"pid":"b7e304456b39e84c34e3fe1862099e817a5f2779","tid":1089706,"uid":157994,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T03:46:12.000Z","msg":"電影界老屎忽"},{"pid":"0240278f18102182cb9632cf8fe317db4c9721ae","tid":1089706,"uid":37524,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b7e304456b39e84c34e3fe1862099e817a5f2779","tid":1089706,"uid":157994,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T03:46:12.000Z","msg":"電影界老屎忽"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T03:49:24.000Z","msg":"老屎怱＋左膠<br />\n簡直係荷里活大毒瘤"},{"pid":"271d18405380559bf1d930ecd0b608924b9be9